  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "一门大炮向远处开火，炮弹划出一道优美的弧线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.49,
      "size": 39888,
      "text": "投篮、喷泉、扔石头，这些抛出去的物体走的都是同一种曲线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "这种运动叫抛体运动，今天我们就来揭开它的秘密。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "decompose",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "decompose-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/decompose-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.89,
      "size": 30240,
      "text": "关键一招：把运动拆成水平和竖直两个方向来看。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "decompose",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "decompose-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/decompose-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "水平方向没有外力，速度不变，做匀速直线运动。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "decompose",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "decompose-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/decompose-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.9,
      "size": 30384,
      "text": "竖直方向只受重力，先减速上升再加速下落。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "parabola",
      "line_id": "par-1",
      "filename": "parabola-par-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/parabola-par-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "水平匀速配上竖直匀变速，合起来正好画出一条抛物线。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "parabola",
      "line_id": "par-2",
      "filename": "parabola-par-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/parabola-par-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.88,
      "size": 30096,
      "text": "飞得越高，落地用的时间就越久，这就是飞行时间。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "parabola",
      "line_id": "par-3",
      "filename": "parabola-par-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/parabola-par-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.81,
      "size": 28944,
      "text": "轨迹左右对称，上升和下落用时完全相同。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "range",
      "line_id": "rng-1",
      "filename": "range-rng-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/range-rng-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.25,
      "size": 36000,
      "text": "射程等于 v0 的平方乘以 sin 二倍角，再除以重力加速度。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "range",
      "line_id": "rng-2",
      "filename": "range-rng-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/range-rng-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.29,
      "size": 36720,
      "text": "当发射角是 45 度时，sin 二倍角取到最大值，射程最远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "range",
      "line_id": "rng-3",
      "filename": "range-rng-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/range-rng-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.08,
      "size": 33264,
      "text": "有趣的是，30 度和 60 度这对互补角，射程完全一样。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "调整初速度，看所有轨迹一起变高变远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.75,
      "size": 27936,
      "text": "对比三个角度，橙色的 45 度总是落得最远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.86,
      "size": 29808,
      "text": "抛体运动能拆成水平匀速与竖直匀变速两部分。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.95,
      "size": 31248,
      "text": "合成的轨迹是抛物线，45 度发射时射程最远。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "projectile-motion",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
      "filename": "summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/projectile-motion/xiaoxiao/summary-sum-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.69,
      "size": 27072,
      "text": "一道弧线里藏着简单的规律，我们下次再见！"
    }
